<details open class="dashboard-details-container" ...attributes>
  <summary class="dashboard-details-container__summary">
    <div class="dashboard-details-container__marker">
      {{svg-jar "caret-right" class="dashboard-details-container__marker-icon" role="presentation"}}
    </div>
  </summary>
  <section class="dashboard-panel">
    <header class="dashboard-panel__header">
      <h3 class="dashboard-panel__header-title">Easy Payments</h3>
      <p class="dashboard-panel__header-desc">DeFi payments that are fast, easy and cheap for everyone</p>
    </header>
    <div class="dashboard-panel__hero" />
    <section class="dashboard-panel__section">
      {{svg-jar "balances-1-customers" width="80" height="80"}}
      <h4 class="dashboard-panel__section-title">Customers</h4>
      <p>You need a prepaid card to pay for products and services offered by merchants in the Card Pay network. To start, you can buy a prepaid card via Apple Pay in the Card Wallet mobile app.</p>
      <ul class="dashboard-panel__list">
        <li>Pay with your prepaid card as you make purchases in the network</li>
        <li>Confirm your payments with Touch ID or Face ID in the Card Wallet mobile app</li>
        <li>Reload your prepaid card at any time</li>
        <li>Earn rewards for the purchases you make</li>
      </ul>
      <Boxel::Button class="dashboard-panel__cta" @kind="primary" @size="touch" @disabled={{true}}>
        Buy Prepaid Card
      </Boxel::Button>
    </section>
    <section class="dashboard-panel__section">
      {{svg-jar "balances-2-issuers" width="80" height="80"}}
      <h4 class="dashboard-panel__section-title">Issuers</h4>
      <p>You can issue prepaid cards yourself, which you can use for purchases in the network or transfer to other users.</p>
      <ul class="dashboard-panel__list">
        <li>Issue your own prepaid card with crypto funding</li>
        <li>Split a prepaid card into several cards of smaller denominations</li>
        <li>Transfer prepaid cards to other users and charge an issuance and/or processing fee</li>
        <li>Reload your prepaid cards by adding more crypto funds</li>
      </ul>
      <Boxel::Button class="dashboard-panel__cta" @kind="primary" @size="touch">
        Issue Prepaid Card
      </Boxel::Button>
      <small class="dashboard-panel__note">
        This is possible if you have a balance of DAI CPXD in your xDai chain wallet. (You can deposit DAI from your mainnet wallet to get a balance of DAI CPXD in your xDai chain wallet.)
      </small>
    </section>
  </section>
</details>